    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一个令人毛骨悚然的体验中，每一关都是一个等待揭开的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在一个黑暗扭曲的梦境中，无尽的走廊和荒凉的房间让你对每一步都产生怀疑。压抑的氛围和诡异的声音让你时刻保持警觉，努力逃离每一个关卡。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.poster.avif?t=1755164314\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.webm?t=1755164314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/484e6dbde0c2357f32c2e7664a625109.mp4?t=1755164314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款受经典“后室”启发的游戏中，每一扇门都是挑战，每一个房间都是威胁。你总感觉有什么在跟着你，而唯一的生存方式就是保持冷静并不断前进，但要小心……你并不总是知道自己正走向何方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在为时已晚之前揭开这些关卡中隐藏的秘密吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本试玩版将带你一窥 2024 年即将到来的恐怖之旅。准备好迷失在未知中，解开谜团，并直面你内心最深的恐惧吧。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.poster.avif?t=1755164314\" width=800 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.webm?t=1755164314\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259880/extras/6c6a84a66a0a9c84d772d3fe9f054cac.mp4?t=1755164314\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
